description_0: A close up view of a worn out, rusted, white iron fire alarm attached to a gray brick wall, made up of thin rectangular shaped bricks placed side by side and stacked on top of each other. The fire alarm has letters embossed onto the top of it, and underneath a star embossed onto it as well, the letters read "STAR SPRINKLER / CORP", the letters are slightly curved into the shape on an upside down U.
description_1: A medium-close-up view of a sculpture of a large ant that is made of a thin metal and is facing right. The body of the ant is made of a bright brown, while the legs are a dark, dull brown. Along the head of the ant, there is a cut out of its eye, and there are two small antennae. Along the back portion of the ant, there are five cutouts that run horizontally, the cutouts are large towards the front and get smaller as they go. Surrounding the bottom portion of the ant are small brown leaves. Behind the ant, there is a large plant that is made up of long blades of grass. Further back, there are 5 square stones that create a walkway. The floor is made up of dark dirt and small twigs. It is daytime, as everything can be seen clearly.
